thread.title: Syl
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Syl

author: Syl
title: Syl
text:
Being in a rural setting, dealing with couriers at a resonable cost can be a challenge.
Items took a while to get picked up but this was no fault of Pack & Send.
They had to rely on a third party courier.
Communication was good and I was kept up to date to when my parcels would be shipped
